results.name: Number of pairwise coprime triples of positive integers with largest element n (i.e., A015617(n) - A015617(n-1)).
reference: Robert Israel, Posting to Sequence Fans Mailing List, Feb 06, 2011
link: Alois P. Heinz, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..10000
mathematica: a[n_] := Sum[Boole[GCD[a, n] == 1 && GCD[b, n] == 1 && GCD[a, b] == 1], {a, 1, n-2}, {b, a+1, n-1}]; Array[a, 100] (* _Jean-François Alcover_, Mar 05 2019, from PARI *)
xref: Cf. A015617. Row sums of triangle A186230. Column 3 of triangle A186972.
